STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Denis A. CATANIA, a/k/a Dennis Catania, Defendant-Petitioner. C-93 September Term 2017
079250 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 27, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-00175-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
